SSL Cerfificate


add thsi to the app.js file on the top:

const fs = require('fs');
var privateKey = fs.readFileSync( 'privatekey.pem' );
var certificate = fs.readFileSync( 'certificate.pem' );

https.createServer({
    key: privateKey,
    cert: certificate
}, app).listen(port);


download the ssl key file from IONOS for example


add the key file to the node app folder




